The Peter Schiff Show
Monday, 15 November 2010


[sebaygo1]


Description from the SchiffRadio web site ::

Peter is back and will interview Christopher Whalen, cofounder of Institutional Risk Analytics. Whalen will argue that the federal government must restructure America's largest banks, as well as discuss his new book, "Inflated: How Money and Debt Built the American Dream". Peter is also looking forward to your calls on politics, finance, and the economy.
